      "content": "\"necessary evil\" sounds pretty extreme though. it's like you're saying the suffering of people today is just something we have to accept for some theoretical future stability. isn't it more accurate to say that both paths have huge risks, rather than just saying debt reduction is the only way to avoid collapse?",
